<% title "Sell merchandise" %>
<% page_md %>
<%= render "events/nav", selected: :documentation %>

<% content_for :head do %>
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="HCB">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://hcb.hackclub.com">
  <meta property="og:title" content="<%= @document_title %>">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="<%= @document_title %>">
  <meta property="og:description" content="<%= @document_subtitle %>">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="<%= @document_subtitle %>">
  <meta name="description" content="<%= @document_subtitle %>">
<% end %>

<div style="padding-top: 2rem;">
  <div class="container container--md">
    <h1 class="mb0" style="border:none"><%= @document_title %></h1>
    <h3 class="mt0 mb2" style="color: gray; font-weight: 500;"><%= @document_subtitle %></h3>
    <%= image_tag @document_image, class: "w-100" if @document_image %>
<%# content starts here %>
    <p>If you raise funds by selling merchandise on online platforms such as Redbubble, Shopify, or Wix, you can deposit your funds into HCB. Follow these steps to get started:</p>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Verify</strong> that the platform you’re using allows for PayPal as a payout option.</li>
      <li>
      <strong>Get familiar with payouts.</strong> Here's what you need to know:
      <ul>
        <li>The frequency of payouts (once a month, twice a month, etc.)</li>
        <li>Any thresholds you need to reach in order to get a payout (ex. no payout until you hit a $20 minimum)</li>
      </ul>
      </li>
      <li><strong>Get in touch with the HCB team.</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>Let us know at <%= help_email %> that you'd like to connect an online merch shop to your HCB account.</li>
          <li>We'll schedule a 15-minute call to get you setup.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <%# "Attention" Card %>
    <div class="card container--sm border b--warning pb0 mt3 mb3 mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-center warning">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 32 32" class="mr1" style="--darkreader-inline-fill: currentColor;" data-darkreader-inline-fill=""><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M26 16c0 5.523-4.477 10-10 10S6 21.523 6 16 10.477 6 16 6s10 4.477 10 10zm2 0c0 6.627-5.373 12-12 12S4 22.627 4 16 9.373 4 16 4s12 5.373 12 12z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path><path d="M16 12.75a1.5 1.5 0 1 0 0-3 1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0 3zM16 22.25c-.552 0-1-.392-1-.875v-6.25c0-.483.448-.875 1-.875s1 .392 1 .875v6.25c0 .483-.448.875-1 .875z"></path></svg>
        <p class="bold mt0 mb0">Important info about payouts:</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="mt1 mb2">
        <li><strong>Notify us when you make a deposit</strong>—we can't fund your account until you reach out.</li>
        <li><strong>PayPal will charge an additional fee</strong> of around 4% or more, on top of the 7% fee.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="border-top card__banner card__darker secondary">
        <strong>Questions?</strong>
        <%= help_message %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p>
      It will be your responsibility to notify the HCB team of the amount of money you’re receiving for each payout. If you are expecting money, <strong>you need to let us know</strong>; otherwise, we will not be able to move funds.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
